title: Did the company overestimate the danger it was in during the Capitol riot?
subtitle: AOC was targeted with another round of malformations of bad intentions immediately after giving an emotional account of its experiments during the Capitol riot.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: Alexandria Okasio Cortez overestimated the danger it was in during the January 6, 2021, riots in the Capitol, as it "was not even in the Capitol Building" when the riot occurred.
